{
  "kg_name": "holdout-v2-pacer-federal-dockets",
  "_source": "CourtListener REST v4 /api/rest/v4/dockets/ (jurisdiction=FD, date_filed 2023-2024). CourtListener is the free open mirror of PACER maintained by the Free Law Project (the RECAP Archive). Raw JSONL staged at benchmarks/datasets/holdout_v2_raw/holdout-v2-pacer-federal-dockets/dockets.jsonl. See scripts/fetch_courtlistener_dockets.py and scripts/prep_pacer_federal_dockets.py.",
